column6: Bowman marries Sisi , becomes the ruler of Gang and has [three] children : Sirharani , Falcon and Ira .

The Transitions Series is a series of fantasy novels by R._A._Salvatore , the famous science fiction and fantasy author , consisting of [three] novels : The Orc King , The Pirate King , and The Ghost King .
